Below is the Java code to determine the self-power number:

```java
public static boolean isSelfPower(int num) {
    int sum = 0;
    int temp = num;
    while(temp > 0) {
        int digit = temp % 10;
        sum += Math.pow(digit, digit);
        temp /= 10;
    }
    return sum == num;
}
```

